<plot>Jason and his friends lead a double life. Bored suburban teens by day, petty thugs by night. In their unsupervised world, anything goes. When Colin and Tony come up with their most devious plan yet, Jason finds himself trying to bring his friends to their senses. When peer pressure wins, Jason soon sees his own words become reality when the plan goes awry. Blood On Our Hands explores the events of four teen friends and the power of peer pressure.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?075663</url></doc>
